snippet.title: Amber Heard says she'll be returning to Aquaman 2 despite rumors
snippet.description: Amber Heard says she's 'so excited' about Aquaman 2.The actress, 34, is dampening rumors she won't be returning to her role as Mera in the second Aquaman film, telling Entertainment Weekly she's ready and rearing to film once more.Heard's comments come after months of unconfirmed rumors she would not be reprising the role from the Jason Momoa-fronted 2018 James Wan superhero hit.   +3   img id="i-d5b10e6ee598ffdc" src="https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/11/12/22/35617662-8944137-Ready_Amber_Heard_says_she_s_so_excited_to_return_as_the_charact-m-23_1605220928314.jpg" height="643" width="634" alt="" class="blkBorder img-share" /  Copy link to paste in your message   'I'm super excited about the amount of fan love and the amount of fan appreciation that Aquaman has acquired and that it has garnered so much excitement for Aquaman and Mera that it means we'll be coming back, she told EW.
